title: Fernhill A5 — the frost-sealed glasshouse door thaws when the boiler runs
story: fernhill
description: The Greenhouse's north exit is blocked while the boiler is off
  (conditional blocked exit reading live switchable state). Turning the boiler
  on flips the condition; the way to Folly Hill (and the warped folly door)
  opens up. (Phase 5 replaces the bare switchable flip with the 3-stage
  machine — this transcript pins the A5 condition itself.)
